quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  79,27,"Ese (yemwe bantu) iremwa ryanyu ni ryo rikomeye, cyangwa ikirere (Allah) yubatse (ni cyo gikomeye)"
  79,28,"Yazamuye igisenge cyacyo, maze aragitunganya"
  79,29,"Ijoro ryacyo arigira umwijima, amanywa yacyo arayakesha"
  79,30,Nyuma y’ibyo arambura isi
  79,31,Ayisohoramo amazi yayo n’inzuri zayo
  79,32,Anashimangira imisozi
  79,33,"Kugira ngo bibagirire akamaro, mwe n’amatungo yanyu"
  79,34,Ariko igihe icyago gihambaye (umunsi w’imperuka) kizaza
  79,35,Umunsi umuntu azibuka ibyo yashyizemo umuhate
  79,36,Umuriro wa Jahanamu ukagaragarizwa (buri wese) ureba
  79,37,Ubwo wa wundi wigometse
  79,38,Agahitamo ubuzima bwo kuri iyi si (agakurikira ibibi aterwa n’irari rye)
  79,39,Mu by’ukuri umuriro wa Jahanamu uzaba ubuturo (bwe)
  79,40,"Ariko wa wundi watinye kuzahagarara imbere ya Nyagasani we, akanabuza umutima we kurarikira ibibi"
  79,41,"Mu by’ukuri, ubusitani (Ijuru) buzaba ubuturo (bwe)"
  79,42,(Abahakanyi) barakubaza (yewe Muhamadi) ku bijyanye n’igihe imperuka izabera
  79,43,Nta bumenyi ufite bwo kugira icyo uyivugaho
  79,44,Ubumenyi bwayo bwihariye Nyagasani wawe
  79,45,Ahubwo wowe (Muhamadi) nta kindi uri cyo uretse kuba uri umuburizi w’abatinya (umunsi w’imperuka)
  79,46,"Umunsi bazawubona, bazamera nk’aho babaye ku isi ikigoroba kimwe cyangwa igitondo kimwe"